{"tid":2320054,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：因為我的手沒有消毒，然後把國旗倒轉，這便屬玷污。","createTime":"2020-12-10T13:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T14:06:30.000Z","uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f83aa6116aa5cf7f57767b0b110e33726a268295","tid":2320054,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ijcEMKD.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FijcEMKD.png&h=5c83a65f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/U2f2wZalhaE?t=242\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FU2f2wZalhaE%3Ft%3D242&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=a66fb29b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/U2f2wZalhaE?t=242</a><br />\n<em>鄭松泰議員：在侮辱國旗的部分，其實有 5 個類近的元素：焚燒、毀損、塗劃、玷污和踐踏，小弟在《國旗及國徽條例》下所干犯的部分是玷污。我的案件在裁判法院審理，<span class=\"gold\">但我沒有錢上訴，我理應就這 5 點提出上訴。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就玷污這一點而言，與其他數個元素一起來看，其實是頗具體地就着國旗的原形、原狀而定，如果令國旗受到具體侮辱，便會觸犯《國旗及國徽條例》，例如焚燒肯定是，因為是燒毀了；毀損，即扯破了，大家理解嗎？塗劃，即在上面劃了東西；踐踏，即踩在它上面，大家都理解嗎？但是，何謂&quot;玷污&quot;呢？<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">小弟所干犯的玷污，便是因為我的手沒有消毒，然後把國旗倒轉，這便屬玷污。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />在《國旗及國徽條例》的實際操作上，有這 5 點作為基本的所謂 indicator(指標)--我說&quot;所謂&quot;，如果這些概念不正確，律師又會指正我--但是，《條例草案》中關於侮辱國歌的罪行可以是&quot;任何方式&quot;，即官方說怎樣便怎樣，大家理解嗎？這是第二個問題。</em><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/counmtg/floor/cm20200604-confirm-ec.pdf#nameddest=mbp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr19-20%2Fchinese%2Fcounmtg%2Ffloor%2Fcm20200604-confirm-ec.pdf%23nameddest%3Dmbp&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqSUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=e9ac27bc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr19-20/chinese/counmtg/floor/cm20200604-confirm-ec.pdf#nameddest=mbp</a>"},{"pid":"6ec94098aeb399ab6e21afdaeb6b9f7460a68fda","tid":2320054,"uid":366470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"立法會唯一反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有得入閘屎都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc4464fd8daf0c2071dbe7ef85eb6fb63e86b0c","tid":2320054,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ec94098aeb399ab6e21afdaeb6b9f7460a68fda","tid":2320054,"uid":366470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:24:07.000Z","msg":"立法會唯一反對派<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有得入閘屎都食<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:26:11.000Z","msg":"鄭松泰議員：其實我個人一向也不太喜歡政治。我說認真的，我一點也不喜歡政治。其實，現在很多市民最關注的問題是：香港有沒有食物可吃，大家有沒有甚麼食物可吃。"},{"pid":"522ebcbcf3cd8393a7b230ea8ee9c86ab740d033","tid":2320054,"uid":61653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"怨婦派虫太"},{"pid":"f87c398430540327e25daa47928f994a200202be","tid":2320054,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"522ebcbcf3cd8393a7b230ea8ee9c86ab740d033","tid":2320054,"uid":61653,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T13:28:26.000Z","msg":"怨婦派虫太"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/ass